1. Install Eclipse Luna (4.4)
   Put eclipse folder in /opt/ and create link in /usr/bin/

2. Download and install eclim
   
$ git clone git://github.com/ervandew/eclim.git
$ cd eclim
$ ant clean deploy -Declipse.home=/opt/eclipse

3. Commands
   start-eclimd
   eclim-project-open
   ...etc

##################################################################

1. Install and configure Maven
   sudo apt-get install maven

   settings.xml
   <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
   <settings ...>
       <servers>
           <server>
				<id>TomcatServer</id>
				<username>admin</username>
				<password>password</password>
	   		</server>
       </servers>
   </settings>

2. Install and configure Tomcat 7
   sudo apt-get install tomcat7 tomcat7-admin

   tomcat-users.xml
   <role rolename="manager-gui"/>
   <role rolename="manager-script"/>
   <user username="admin" password="password" roles="manager-gui,manager-script" />

3. Add tomcat7 plugin to projects pom.xml

       	<plugin>
			<groupId>org.apache.tomcat.maven</groupId>
			<artifactId>tomcat7-maven-plugin</artifactId>
			<version>2.2</version>
			<configuration>
				<url>http://localhost:8080/manager/text</url>
				<server>TomcatServer</server>
				<path>/APP_NAME</path>
			</configuration>
	    </plugin>


4. Commands

mvn tomcat7:deploy 
mvn tomcat7:undeploy 
mvn tomcat7:redeploy
